FBIS4-38831 "drsov107_a_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Kim Says Yeltsin To Visit ROK Kim Says Yeltsin To Visit ROK SK0306084394 Seoul YONHAP in English 0701 GMT 3 Jun 94 SK0306084394 Seoul YONHAP English BFN [Text] Moscow, June 3 (YONHAP) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin will visit South Korea in the near future, President Kim Yong-sam said Friday [3 June]. Kim told South Korean correspondents here that Yeltsin had accepted his invitation to visit Seoul and expected that it would take place soon. Considering that Yeltsin's term of office expires in June 1996, he is expected to visit South Korea next year, a senior member of Kim's entourage said.
